https://app.opus.com/app/workflow/share/f0263c56-2554-4294-9d92-090264afb436

This workflow schedules a daily check of a given URL, retrieves its content, extracts any available offer and price information, detects price drops by comparing current and previous prices, determines if a notification is required, and sends an email notification to the specified address if an offer or price drop is detected.
Industry
Retail & E-commerce - Retail Analytics

Inputs & Outputs
Input

The URL to be monitored for offers or price drops.

The specific time of day to perform the daily check (in 24-hour format, e.g., '14:00').

The email address to send notifications to if an offer or price drop is detected.

Output
Status of the notification email, including whether it was sent, the recipient, and the reason.
